<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to Soseki App</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
        .credentials { margin: 20px 0; padding: 15px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 20px; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #4F46E5; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Welcome to Soseki App!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
            <p>An administrator has created a new account for you on Soseki App.</p>
            <p>Here are your temporary login credentials. We strongly recommend changing your password after logging in for the first time.</p>
            
            <div class="credentials">
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
                <p><strong>Password:</strong> {{password}}</p>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="btn" style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;">Log In Now</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Soseki App. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
